---
title: SEV-1 Incident Response Flow: Friday 5 PM Scenario
---
flowchart LR
    t0["T+0 alert storm<br/>HTTP 500 12%, DB pool exhausted, gateway timeout 35%"]
    sev1["T+30s classify SEV-1<br/>data/payment integrity risk"]
    warroom["T+2m open war room<br/>assign IC, Scribe, Comms, SRE"]
    rollback["T+5m rollback canary<br/>route traffic to stable, freeze releases"]
    comm["T+5–15m communications<br/>internal, status page, leadership"]
    verify["T+10–15m verify recovery<br/>5xx, DB pool, payment success, synthetics"]
    root["Root cause<br/>hotfix bypassed staging and gates"]
    post["Postmortem + controls<br/>block bypass, stronger RBAC, audit evidence"]
    t0 --> sev1
    sev1 --> warroom
    sev1 --> rollback
    warroom --> comm
    rollback --> verify
    comm --> verify
    verify --> root
    root --> post
